      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections, and is protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. No modifications, no accidents, and a spotless history\u2014this car is for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
